Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:09.75,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:20.28,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,…gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,…but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I’ve made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.47,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:06.95,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:14.22,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:20.96,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,…a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair… Don’t you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:28.39,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:31.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,As planned…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:34.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,…with communication cables\Nintact, Chor Tempest…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,…will descend as low as possible…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:39.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and protect the Ruins from attack\Nby the Shoukoku-highland forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:49.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:55.34,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The Funeral
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:05.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,This sibylla’s spirit is\Nbound by chains of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:10.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, both the merciful\NTempus Spatium, as well as Kyuukoku…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:12.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,…are prepared to\Nforgive and accept her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:36.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why the heck was Anglas lying\Ndead inside an ancient Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,That day, there’s no\Nquestion that she…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:45.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,They never found so much as\Na bone fragment in the debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:07.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,This sibylla has just received\Nthe divine grace of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:11.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that she is about to set off\Non a new journey, let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was a highland priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can we hold a funeral\Nfor her on the Arcus Prima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,The high priestess felt it\Nwas the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,And how did the\Nmilitary council feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,That since the Highlands and\NShoukoku are now allies…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:55.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,…it wouldn’t do to send\Neven the remains back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,And yet they’re so full\Nof mutual animosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it seems they do agree\Non the most unlikely thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that’s what\Ncauses trouble for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,You won’t get a\Nbreeze sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:27.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think that you’d start a\Nconversation with me… Who knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened at the Ruins…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,We found the Spring\Ninside the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,And Onasia was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,…the Spring itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s just like Grandpa said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,And then we found Anglas, who\Nsurely perished in that explosion…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,…inside an ancient Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:21.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m thinking that Anglas\Nwent there herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:23.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that moment…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,…the moment the Simoun exploded…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,…she went to a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,A different…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:31.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,…world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just when we thought we were\Nback home on the Arcus Prima…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,…all these weird\Nthings started happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,At least give us a\Nlittle downtime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,There’s no time to get comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:48.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re to go to the maju\Npool right after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:50.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do like majus…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,…but not if we’re\Nbeing ordered to do them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:55.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn’t that Neviril\Nand Aer over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:01.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, so they managed to make up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril was just having\Na hissy fit on her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:22.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Aer. What do you mean by…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s something Grandpa told me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is as far as I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:42.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:44.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Getting old means making\Nmore and more choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:52.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,And with every choice you make…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:55.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,…you erase all\Nother possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don’t understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun will show\Nyou where you’re headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:03.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where I’m headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,To a different world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:15.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,What my grandpa meant by\Nthat, I still don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Grandpa was\Nalways yearning for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:21.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, is that why you never\Nwanted to choose your gender?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,The helical motors…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Said to manipulate\Nboth time and space…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought it was\Nno more than a story…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,…to strengthen the\Nmystery of the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,“Everywhere…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and yet nowhere.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that’s true of Onasia…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and true of Anglas…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and true of the Simouns…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,…it’s true of Rimone\Nand Dominüra as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we just talked about…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s keep it between ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we’re going to share a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:18.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why didn’t you attend\NAnglas’s funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:19.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,A priestess from a\Nlowly family like mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:24.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,…has no right to\Nattend a holy ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,B-But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,— You joined us the other time.\N— Things are different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our leaders are in turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:33.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,But they allowed an enemy\Npriestess’s funeral to be held here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t sound\Nlike yourself at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought you\Nliked that Anglas girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew I’d have to face at least\Nthis level of discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:51.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only reason I got to the rank\Nof Simoun sibylla was because…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:54.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I had the backing\Nof the vice chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the vice chancellor has changed.
Comment: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:04.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,He’s nothing but a\Nsenile old geezer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute, Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:09.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed our time on the Messis,\Nespecially that mouse stew I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:10.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:13.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Watching all you oh-so-noble\Npriestesses taste that stew…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:16.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I thought, “Hey, they’re\Njust the same as me!”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s right. We’re the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:20.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re not the same after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:37.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,The maju pool is under the\Njurisdiction of the chancellors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Should you set foot in this area…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,— …the high priestess will…\N— It doesn’t matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Military Councilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must forgive us…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,…but we can’t have\Nso many observers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,It will disturb our prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,A maju is not a prayer.
Comment: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:09.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is battle practice,\NSibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’d like to see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:20.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,What Chor Tempest is\Ncurrently capable of…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ri Majon with the\Nmost destructive power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a lovely wake\Nthey’re creating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Dandelion Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one that harms no one…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,…that leads no one astray…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,…the one for ceremonies…
Comment: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:55.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the one for ceremonies...\NHmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn’t make the\Nwrong choice after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Entrusting Aer to\Nbecome Neviril’s pair…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:22.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it’s all good\Nbecause of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,You have no clue whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:29.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could the judgment of\Nsomeone who’s been asleep…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,…be less questionable\Nthan your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thinking someone\Nlike you can protect her…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,…is gross arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:41.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,…let Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I might have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,With you…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I might have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to pair up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:15.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all, I’m the one who\Nshould be protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dismantle a Simoun…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:57.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought I’d hear those\Nwords from anyone else but you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,…Sibylla Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forget about that day, Waporif.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s the last warning\NI’ll be giving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,But how could I ever forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,“Without something to believe in…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:17.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,…none of us can even\Nplant our feet on the earth.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you found\Nsomething to believe in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:35.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should I believe in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:51.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have ordered\Nthe maintenance crew…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,…to dismantle the ancient\NSimoun as you instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:57.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dismantling a divine vessel.\NHow sacrilegious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which is more sacrilegious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:03.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Allowing our holy Tempus Spatium\Nto be tainted by outsiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,The topic for discussion today…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,…is what to do about\Nthat enemy air base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:14.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,As most of the ancient Simouns\Nare now in the enemy’s hands…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I believe it would be\Ndangerous to send Chor Tempest…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:20.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,— …out on a reconnaissance mission…\N— Then when would you deem it safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:24.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand your concern for\Nyour daughter’s well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, should another\Nincident occur…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:31.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,…next time for sure, you won’t have\Na leg to stand on, Vice Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who is paired up with Sibylla Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,That would be Sibylla Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Out of all the members\Nof Chor Tempest…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:42.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,…she has no parallel\Nas an auriga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I recall, her grandfather was…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so, she herself…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anglas’s funeral is long over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:10.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shouldn’t she have been committed\Nto the earth as soon as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is an order from\Nthe military councilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The military councilor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,How dare you debase a departed\Nspirit. I won’t allow this to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:33.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Once you’ve left the cockpit of a\NSimoun, a woman is utterly powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,It would be too\Ndangerous to sit back…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:49.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and do nothing about\Nthat mobile air base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:54.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are hereby sending Chor Tempest\Non a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Messis shall serve\Nas the relay point…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:16:00.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? Just when we finally got away\Nfrom that musty, old rust bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am happy to welcome\Nyou all back, Sibyllae!
Comment: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:04.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if we discover the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,That will be left to\Nyour discretion, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:10.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:15.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I do believe you have the\Ncapacity to blow it up at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:20.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,As both Sibylla Dominüra and Sibylla\NRimone are missing in action…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:23.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,…we will have to\Nreadjust your pairings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:27.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta and Sibylla Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Alty and Sibylla Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Roatreamon and Sibylla Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and Sibylla Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Yun and Sibylla Aer…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:47.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s been decided that you two will\Nsit out this particular mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:51.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWhy am I being left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer is my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’ll have to convince me as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:03.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:07.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, don’t cause\Nany more trouble for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s the matter?\NYou can’t sleep, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:31.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your maju this afternoon.\NIt was magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:40.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,How about… a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry. I’m not in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:08.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought you’d\Nstand up for Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s not that I’ve opened\Nup to her completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,But by coming face\Nto face with Aer…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I’m also coming face\Nto face with Amuria…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,…meaning I’m facing\Nup to myself as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:25.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,That may have been my\Ngreatest fear all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:30.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I was just trying to avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:34.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve allowed you all to\Nhumor me far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:36.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,So let me humor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:40.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can go ahead\Nand lean on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,But at this rate…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I won’t make it to a different world.
Comment: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:50.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I won't make it to a different world.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing, never mind\Nwhat I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,A different world, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,If it’s a different\Nworld you long for…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,…then I’ll show you one now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:08.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Parai…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun’s fast asleep, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:09.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just thought you might\Nbe too nervous to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:12.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pairing up with Sibylla Aurea…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:17.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I always saw that as the\Nfastest way to achieve my goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don’t want you\Nto get the wrong idea.
Comment: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:21.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:25.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Deep down, I do want the rest\Nof you to see me as an equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,…not for the same\Nreasons as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s because…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,…I really want to be\Nfriends with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:43.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,So stop saying things like,\N“We’re friends,” will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s just a matter of\Nhow you feel about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:48.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:53.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, do you want me\Nto sing you a lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:56.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean the one\Nyou sang for Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!\NI’m not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:05.08,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Hear the echo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:07.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry, not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:12.00,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,…of the swirling light…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:24.65,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,…bringing us tales of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:36.45,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Proof that an\Neternal world exists…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:43.19,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,…shall be revealed\Nby Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:51.53,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Rocking gently until\Nwe awake tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why do you think they\Ntook you off the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:50.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:51.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,You do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,There’s something that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:57.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t tell you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,…because I promised not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:00.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:02.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s wise of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:06.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Promises are made\Nto be kept after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:22.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve got to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,As do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:47.78,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds…\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:52.02,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:59.09,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon’t be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:23:06.68,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart’s overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:19.57,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,“I want to get closer to you.”\N“I want to feel your pulse.”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.57,0:23:24.75,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:28.72,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:32.76,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart’s desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:38.63,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can’t reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:44.17,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the\Nsky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:47.61,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:53.27,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:59.50,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to “now” the way it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.71,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:08.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril’s Simoun is shot down…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:13.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and forced to make an emergency\Nlanding on Shoukoku’s aerial base.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:15.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:17.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:20.02,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Sibylla
